snippet.title: Dublin - The Pembroke Clinic
snippet.description: Dublin - The Pembroke Clinic Established in 1988. The Pembroke Clinic, situated beside the Ulster Bank on the corner of Lwr Baggot St & Lwr Pembroke St, is one of the longest established Medical Practices in the D2 area. Resident Doctors, Dr. Edward Kennedy and Dr. Gillian Darling offer wide experience in the fields of General Practice, Women's health care and travel vaccinations.
